OL,3,CPrincipal gives evidence at trial of
OL,4,Cschool's welfare officer
OL,6,FThe principal of Lagan College was
OL,7,Fcalled to give evidence today
OL,8,F(Thursday) at a trial concerning the
OL,9,Falleged conduct of the south Belfast
OL,10,Fschool's health and welfare officer.
OL,12,FNeil Clarke Beckett - who is currently
OL,13,Fsuspended from his position - has been
OL,14,Faccused by nine pupils of sexual
OL,15,Foffences.
OL,17,FAll nine complainants have now given
OL,18,Fevidence at the trial, which is being
OL,19,Fheld at Belfast Crown Court.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
