OL,3,CPrincipal gives evidence at trial of
OL,4,Cschool's welfare officer
OL,6,FToday, the jury of six men and six
OL,7,Fwomen heard evidence from the school
OL,8,Fprincipal regarding what steps where
OL,9,Ftaken in the aftermath of the
OL,10,Fallegations made against Beckett.
OL,12,FThe 43 year-old, from Kilmore Village
OL,13,Fnear Downpatrick, denies 29 sexual
OL,14,Foffences spanning a period from 2013
OL,15,Fto 2023.
OL,17,FThese allegations concern nine pupils
OL,18,Fat the school as well as two Army
OL,19,FCadets who claim they were abused by
OL,20,FBeckett whilst he occupied a role as
OL,21,Ftheir leader.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
