OL,3,CPrincipal gives evidence at trial of
OL,4,Cschool's welfare officer
OL,6,FLagan College Principal Amanda McNamee
OL,7,Fconfirmed Beckett commenced his
OL,8,Fposition as the school's health and
OL,9,Fwelfare officer in August 2021.
OL,11,FQuestioned about the first time she
OL,12,Fbecame aware of allegations concerning
OL,13,FBeckett, Mrs McNamee said that in
OL,14,FOctober 2022 two pupils spoke to
OL,15,Fmembers of staff.
OL,17,FShe said one girl reported that
OL,18,FBeckett had given her a hug and kissed
OL,19,Fher on the cheek whilst another girl
OL,20,Ftold a teacher Beckett had given her a
OL,21,Fhug under her blazer.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
