OL,3,CPrincipal gives evidence at trial of
OL,4,Cschool's welfare officer
OL,6,FShe confirmed that she reminded
OL,7,FBeckett of the need to ensure "a
OL,8,Fplatinum standard of boundaries", the
OL,9,Fschool's safeguarding policy regarding
OL,10,Fchildren and his role within the
OL,11,Fschool.
OL,13,FThe role, she said, included First Aid
OL,14,Fbut did not amount to counselling and
OL,15,Fthat Beckett told her he felt
OL,16,F"overwhelmed... he said he sometimes
OL,17,Ffelt a little bit uncertain as to what
OL,18,Fhis role was".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
