OL,6,FShe was then questioned about what
OL,7,Fhappened in January 2023 and Mrs
OL,8,FMcNamee confirmed a pupil attended a
OL,9,Fmeeting at the school with her mother.
OL,11,FThe pupil's mother alleged Beckett had
OL,12,Ftouched her daughter inappropriately
OL,13,Fin the school's hygiene room and that
OL,14,Fshe wanted the matter referred to the
OL,15,FPSNI.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
