OL,6,FWhen asked at that point if Beckett
OL,7,Fwas "withdrawn from any role in the
OL,8,FCollege that would give him direct
OL,9,Faccess to students", the principal
OL,10,Fsaid "yes, that was the action I took
OL,11,Fimmediately".
OL,13,FShe also confirmed she told Beckett
OL,14,Fthe nature of the allegation and that
OL,15,Fhe denied it and said the only time he
OL,16,Ftouched her was to hand her a plaster.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
