OL,6,FThe jury heard that following this,
OL,7,Fthe matter was referred to the
OL,8,FChairman of the Board of Governors and
OL,9,Fthe Education Authority and that
OL,10,FBeckett was placed on precautionary
OL,11,Fsuspension.
OL,13,FWhen asked if Beckett was upset, Mrs
OL,14,FMcNamee said "yes, he was very upset".
OL,16,FA strategy meeting was then held and
OL,17,Fthe matter was referred to the PSNI.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
