OL,6,FThe Crown barrister then asked what
OL,7,Fhappened at the start of February 2023
OL,8,Fand she said she was informed of
OL,9,Ffurther allegations made by another
OL,10,Fpupil regarding Beckett which were
OL,11,Falso forwarded to the PSNI "as soon as
OL,12,Fthey were received".
OL,14,FMrs McNamee was also questioned by
OL,15,Fdefence barrister Laura Ievers KC, who
OL,16,Fsuggested that after concerns were
OL,17,Fraised in October 2022 Beckett wasn't
OL,18,Ftold who the two pupils were but he
OL,19,Frequested they were not sent to him in
OL,20,Fthe future.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
